            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "After being idled for a few weeks, production of the Chevrolet Camaro and other GM cars will resume once again at the Lansing Grand River Assembly plant. As we reported back in March, ",
